"link> is made by <link xlink:href=\"http://www.linux-on-laptops.com/\"></"
"link>. Information about laptops and handhelds can be found here."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: mobile.xml:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&suse; maintains a mailing list in German dedicated to the subject of "
"laptops. See <link xlink:href=\"http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-mobile-de/"
"\"></link>. On this list, users and developers discuss all aspects of mobile "
"computing with &productname;. Postings in English are answered, but the "
"majority of the archived information is only available in German. Use <link "
"xlink:href=\"http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-mobile/\"></link> for "
"English postings."
msgstr ""
